high_descs: Go forward and go around the island to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up the yellow knife from the counter.
Move over right to the red tomato on the counter between the knife and the spatula.
Slice a half of the tomato on the counter.
Place the knife on the counter in front of the tomato.
Take one slice of the tomato from the counter.
Turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Remove the tomato slice after it's been chilled on the middle shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn right and go back to the counter with the sliced tomato on top.
Place the chilled tomato slice on the counter in front of the rest of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of tomato on the counter.
